latestIgtvVideos.title: Homemade Green Thai Curry
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Unmute for procedure!
Ingredients :
2 medium sized onions, chopped
2 spring onions, chopped
5-7 cloves of garlic
4-5 green chillies
A fistful of coriander 
1 inch of ginger 
2 tbsp oil
1/2 Carrot,chopped 
A handful of Broccoli florets
1/4 of both green and yellow Zucchini , chopped 
1/4 of each Red , yellow and green capsicum , chopped 
2-3 Baby corns,chopped 
1-1.5 cups coconut milk (see the end to see how to make it from scratch)
1/4 tsp lemon zest 
A small bunch of lemon grass 

Coconut milk recipe:
Take two mature coconuts and keep them in the fridge for a while.
This ensures that upon cracking the coconut open , we can extract the white portion easily .
Collect the coconut water.
Extract the white flesh of the coconut using a knife , it’ll be easier to slide it out of the coconuts are refrigerated.
Blend the white part of the 2 coconuts with 1.5 cups of water . 
Once blended, use a muslin cloth to filter the mixture and collect the coconut milk . 
The milk is ready to use!

latestIgtvVideos.title: Healthy Pre-Dinner Salad
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Ingredients 
-half cup of sliced carrots 
-half cup of boiled broccoli florets 
-Half cup of sliced cucumber
-Half of a sliced yellow /red/green capsicum
(Chop the vegetables and refrigerate 30 minutes in advance to maintain their crunch)
-6 to 7 black pitted  olives
-8-10 cubes of tofu 
-some coarsely chopped lettuce
-3-4 minced garlic cloves 
-A tablespoon of olive oil 
-teaspoon of Italian seasoning 
-Half teaspoon of black pepper 
-Half teaspoon of chilli flakes 
-Salt to taste
-A tablespoon of channa jor 
-2 tablespoons of roasted peanuts 
-Juice of one and a half lemon 
Toss all the ingredients together for a healthy and nutritious salad 🥗
